text: Dave England (born December 30, 1969) is an American stunt performer and actor. He is known for his works in Jackass and for all of its movies. England was born in Ventura, California. ==Movies== *Jackass: The Movie (2002) *Jackass: Number Two (2006) *Jackass 2.5 (2007) *Shred (2008) *Shred 2 (2009) *Jackass 3D (2010) *Jackass 3.5 (2011) ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American television personalities Category:Actors from Ventura County, California Category:People from Ventura, California Category:Stunt performers
